OL,3,CPlans for food hall unveiled as new
OL,4,Cowners take on Carlisle Market Hall
OL,6,FCarlisle's historic Market Hall has
OL,7,Fbeen acquired by a new owner, with
OL,8,Fbosses promising to "breathe new life"
OL,9,Finto the site.
OL,11,FWelsh property developer Bearmont
OL,12,FGroup has acquired the lease for the
OL,13,Fpremises which include the indoor
OL,14,Fmarket, the TK Maxx building and the
OL,15,Funit formally occupied by Wilko.
OL,17,FMason Partners will manage the day-to-
OL,18,Fday running of the site after being
OL,19,Fjointly appointed by Bearmont Group
OL,20,Fand Cumberland Council.
