OL,3,CPlans for food hall unveiled as new
OL,4,Cowners take on Carlisle Market Hall
OL,6,FIt comes as the council is exploring
OL,7,Foptions to improve the facility,
OL,8,Fincluding creating a new food hall
OL,9,Fwhich it hopes would attract more
OL,10,Fvisitors.
OL,12,FWhat is being proposed for the site?
OL,14,FInitial plans - submitted to council
OL,15,Fplanners - would remove some existing
OL,16,Fmarket stalls to create a new seated
OL,17,Farea in the centre of the market hall.
