OL,3,CPlans for food hall unveiled as new
OL,4,Cowners take on Carlisle Market Hall
OL,6,FExisting market stalls around the
OL,7,Fperimeter of the building would remain
OL,8,Fand "are well placed to serve the new
OL,9,Fcentral seating area", according to
OL,10,Fthe application submitted earlier this
OL,11,Fmonth.
OL,13,FThe proposal also states that the
OL,14,Fdesigns would allow for the
OL,15,Finstallation of a stage to provide a
OL,16,Ftemporary performance space, including
OL,17,Ffor live music.
