OL,3,CPlans for food hall unveiled as new
OL,4,Cowners take on Carlisle Market Hall
OL,6,FCumberland Council says "Some concept
OL,7,Fdesigns for a communal seating area
OL,8,Fwere included in the application to
OL,9,Fprovide some context, however, these
OL,10,Fdesigns need to be developed further,
OL,11,Fand the council looks forward to
OL,12,Fworking with the traders and
OL,13,Fstallholders as a key part of that
OL,14,Fprocess".
OL,16,FCumberland Councillor Barbara Cannon,
OL,17,Fexecutive member for financial
OL,18,Fplanning and assets, said: "These
OL,19,Frecent developments at The Market Hall
OL,20,Fare really positive news for Carlisle
OL,21,Fand the wider Cumberland area.
