OL,9,Fdevelop the site and help it reach its
OL,10,Ffull potential.
OL,12,F"The Market Hall presents a huge
OL,13,Fopportunity to create an exciting
OL,14,Fdestination for residents and visitors
OL,15,Fthat would contribute to the vitality
OL,16,Fand sustainability of Carlisle city
OL,17,Fcentre.
