OL,3,CPlans for food hall unveiled as new
OL,4,Cowners take on Carlisle Market Hall
OL,6,F"It's been a much-loved part of the
OL,7,Fcity's retail offer for generations
OL,8,Fand we're excited to see what the
OL,9,Ffuture holds."
OL,11,F'A new lease of life'
OL,13,FRob Lloyd, CEO of Bearmont Group,
OL,14,Fshared his vision for the site: "The
OL,15,FMarket Hall represents the heart of
OL,16,FCarlisle's retail experience, and we
OL,17,Fsee a tremendous opportunity to bring
OL,18,Fnew energy to this historic site.
