OL,3,CPlans for food hall unveiled as new
OL,4,Cowners take on Carlisle Market Hall
OL,6,F"This is part of our strategic
OL,7,Fapproach - identifying shopping
OL,8,Fcentres that have lost their way and
OL,9,Fgiving them a new lease of life.
OL,11,F"We'll be working closely with
OL,12,FCumberland Council to breathe new life
OL,13,Finto the indoor market, with an
OL,14,Femphasis on introducing more local
OL,15,Fartisan businesses and an expanded
OL,16,Ffood offering.
OL,18,F"We've already received interest from
OL,19,Fprospective tenants for the former
OL,20,FWilko site, and we hope to announce
OL,21,Ffurther developments shortly."
