OL,3,CPlans for food hall unveiled as new
OL,4,Cowners take on Carlisle Market Hall
OL,6,FMr Lloyd added that Bearmont would
OL,7,Fhope to combine traditional retail
OL,8,Fwith a fresh and modern approach.
OL,10,F"Markets today need to inspire people
OL,11,Fto visit; we're looking at introducing
OL,12,Fmore artisan vendors, like butchers,
OL,13,Ffishmongers, and bakers, to restore
OL,14,Fthat personal, vibrant atmosphere
OL,15,Fwhere shoppers can enjoy unique,
OL,16,Fquality goods and genuine
OL,17,Finteractions," he said.
